author: George Fuller
title: Fishermen land monster stingray after long battle in Thai river
text:
F ishermen land a monster stingray in the Mae Klong River, Thailand.
Yuri Grisendi battled the beast for almost two hours before being able to examine it.
The freshwater stingray weighs 530-pounds and measures two metres across.
After enjoying a few moments of admiration the fishermen release the beast.
